name: 凯尔希·傅莫斯特
name_full: 凯尔希·傅莫斯特 Kelsey Formost
introduction: Kelsey Formost is an actress, singer, and writer based in Hollywood, CA. She received a full-ride scholarship to Davidson College in NC where she worked with the Royal Shakespeare Company and began her film career. A veteran of the stage as well as the screen, she made her Off-Broadway Debut in 'Sleep No More'. Kelsey is a graduate of UCB improv school and also writes her own sketch comedy. She is currently developing two original comedy pilots.
